## how to run locally

```
gem install bundler

bundle install

bundle exec jekyll server

```


## how to put the picture into middle centre

add html flag like this "<img src="" style="display:block;margin:auto"/>"


## how to create a gallery post

```
---
layout: photo
title: Gallery Post
photos:
- http://i.minus.com/ibobbTlfxZgITW.jpg
- http://i.minus.com/iedpg90Y0exFS.jpg
---

```


## how to extract the abstract from the full article

use `<!--more-->` to split


## how to colorize  the code

```bash
ls
pwd

```

